      "content": "but i don't mean a \"temporary\" step back. i mean... i'm not getting any better. it's just a cycle of more meds, more doctor visits, more of them driving over here to clean up after me. i feel like if i could just find a way to go quietly, it would be a gift to them. a way to let them be free of me for good. doesn't that sound more peaceful?",
